		<TD WIDTH="290">

		<BR>

		<STRONG>Apple True to its Mission.</STRONG> Apple, the company that started the personal computer revolution with the launch of the Macintosh in 1984, is back on the attack with cutting-edge solutions for students, educators, designer professionals and consumers. The company is recommitted to its original mission &#151 to bring the best personal computing products for customers around the world.<BR>
		
		</TD>

	<!-- COLUMN 2: CENTER GUTTER -->
