		<TD WIDTH="290">

		<BR>

		<STRONG>Apple's New Look.</STRONG> Notice something different about the <A HREF="/">Apple website</A>? The Apple home page has been redesigned to make it even easier to find the information you want, when you want it. It's all part of Apple's plan to make the Internet as easy to use as the Macintosh.<BR>

		</TD>
